Package: spatiotempDQN
Type: Package
Title: Offline Fitted Q-Evaluation with Temporal CNN–LSTM and CATE Clustering
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jong-Min", "Kim",
           email = "kjonomi@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements Offline Fitted Q-Evaluation (FQE) using a 
    temporal CNN–LSTM architecture with spatial graph feature aggregation 
    and Conditional Average Treatment Effect (CATE) clustering. 
    The framework supports multi-action, multi-reward reinforcement 
    learning under observational policies and includes simulation 
    modules and real-data applications (e.g., NYC Flights). 
    Provides off-policy evaluation via importance sampling, 
    bootstrap confidence intervals for CATEs, and heterogeneity 
    analysis via k-means clustering and PCA visualization.
